.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-690110454122986v - 720x1280 (DASH video)"}, {"format_id": "dash-964223196086659v", "ext": "mp4", "width": 1080, "height": 1920, "tbr": 470.234, "format_note": "DASH video", "container": "mp4_dash", "vcodec": "vp09.00.40.08.00.01.01.01.00", "acodec": "none", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "url": "https://instagram.fkul19-2.fna.fbcdn.net/o1/v/t2/f2/m367/AQMiHz1bNsyN29RZrTL_5ZH7l--3Auq7SCbRxItvpymQFH2_DL0iJu2xA7-ZlSVDmA5zDgkvr7sYj8G-o_2RmV2qI5Yjgc-q-VkUI9E.mp4?_nc_cat=101&_nc_oc=AdrNJOqf2dZgX2hiXsFra55yLOkmmbTNt9JTq3GwKtbK5ICKCbI5fJCPtZguCEaZpsk&_nc_sid=9ca052&_nc_ht=instagram.fkul19-2.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_ohc=XjAP-XT8r3cQ7kNvwEqaDNU&&ccb=17-1&_nc_gid=bMCp15ikGWtcTLAF7v-vgw&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ss=7a22e&oh=00_Af4gt8fDOWXLyjdyGNKyL3Z_HdtcnQyOFtfLP0KwdSbcPw&oe=6A0B2016", "manifest_stream_number": 0, "is_dash_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 470.234, "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 3406845, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-964223196086659v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by daytrading", "description": "Raoul Pal, former Goldman Sachs executive and founder of Real Vision, says AI is making knowledge worth close to zero because information is no longer scarce. \n\nAnyone can access complex answers instantly using AI, removing the advantage people once had from simply knowing more than others. \n\nThis does not mean people lose value, but that the advantage shifts to judgment, creativity, and execution. In the AI era, success will depend less on what you know and more on how you use AI to build, decide, and act faster than everyone else.\n\nFollow @daytrading for daily updates on crypto, stocks, tech, and business.\n\nMedia: A Diary Of A CEO", "duration": 57.96, "timestamp": 1772112218, "uploader_id": "62902870086", "uploader": "Day Trading", "channel": "daytrading", "like_count": 30125, "comment_count": 474, "comments": [{"author": "billy_hunt_63", "author_id": "76807584856", "id": "18090661772252464", "text": "Does AI know how my feet feel after a long walk?", "timestamp": 1777626122}, {"author": "billy_hunt_63", "author_id": "76807584856", "id": "18006571985909094", "text": "Can't see it myself.", "timestamp": 1777626001}, {"author": "adie_lloyd", "author_id": "377294488", "id": "17858232234651372", "text": "I would argue that agriculture is the greatest. There would ne no civilisation without it. But that's immaterial, these tech bros are a death cult that are actively trying to destroy humanity while making as much money as possible. They want to sit on piles of money as the planet burns. They all need to go to the guillotine before its too late.", "timestamp": 1777566314}, {"author": "codu57", "author_id": "2766017599", "id": "17912297190381393", "text": "", "timestamp": 1777469347}, {"author": "getyouaninterview", "author_id": "74167553411", "id": "18032690210796934", "text": "He’s wrong. Applied knowledge is now worth more than gold. Ethereal “knowledge” I guess is free-ish, but this is a gross generalization", "timestamp": 1777421960}, {"author": "macedo_physique", "author_id": "65486825388", "id": "17948135742149795", "text": "People get paid because how they interpret the knowledge not the knowledge itself and that’s a skill that has to be taught.", "timestamp": 1777342206}, {"author": "hotpinkpandabear", "author_id": "4075211605", "id": "18135090151544140", "text": "AI SUCKS... What a waste of energy and resources. 🗽🇺🇸", "timestamp": 1777326623}, {"author": "doc_martinz", "author_id": "15155135386", "id": "18180808057385632", "text": "But they cannot extract emotion.", "timestamp": 1777145660}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://instagram.fkul19-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.71878-15/642170985_2317449705347913_6553219394586987210_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDAuc2RyLnZpZGVvX25mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=instagram.fkul19-2.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=109&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFIbT0nWBRkK-xao-1c7h4sPeXDz6heT90eRrta22Az1kCOv_OoUsrM0NpvEdE8e3s&_nc_ohc=e6lta8_sW4oQ7kNvwHVpRNC&_nc_gid=bMCp15ikGWtcTLAF7v-vgw&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af754aIMV9L4F8RcTWrFgPJW3oTH9m75x4qs43JiCVO2XQ&oe=6A0B1F1A&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://instagram.fkul19-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.71878-15/642170985_2317449705347913_6553219394586987210_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDAuc2RyLnZpZGVvX25mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=instagram.fkul19-2.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=109&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFIbT0nWBRkK-xao-1c7h4sPeXDz6heT90eRrta22Az1kCOv_OoUsrM0NpvEdE8e3s&_nc_ohc=e6lta8_sW4oQ7kNvwHVpRNC&_nc_gid=bMCp15ikGWtcTLAF7v-vgw&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af754aIMV9L4F8RcTWrFgPJW3oTH9m75x4qs43JiCVO2XQ&oe=6A0B1F1A&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1331, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1331"}, {"url": "https://instagram.fkul19-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.71878-15/642170985_2317449705347913_6553219394586987210_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDAuc2RyLnZpZGVvX25mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=instagram.fkul19-2.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=109&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFIbT0nWBRkK-xao-1c7h4sPeXDz6heT90eRrta22Az1kCOv_OoUsrM0NpvEdE8e3s&_nc_ohc=e6lta8_sW4oQ7kNvwHVpRNC&_nc_gid=bMCp15ikGWtcTLAF7v-vgw&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af754aIMV9L4F8RcTWrFgPJW3oTH9m75x4qs43JiCVO2XQ&oe=6A0B1F1A&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 1080, "height": 1917, "id": "2", "resolution":